{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act9mini", "eventName": "红松林", "entryType": "MINI_ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "隨風飄蕩", "storyInfo": "年輕的欣特萊雅在尋找自己今後的人生道路，在年齡與閱歷增長之後，她兀然發現，自己早已沒了選擇的權力，只能隨著時代的潮流不斷飄蕩。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_kxstreet", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204na_platnm_1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在順利結束了學生時代後。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我，欣特萊雅，正在選擇自己的人生道路。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在卡西米爾，學生們結束學業後的人生選擇多種多樣。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "參加大公司每年一度的全國性校招，和全卡西米爾的優秀人才競爭，獲得一份勞累且堪堪糊口的工作。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又或是加入軍隊，經過一年的地獄式訓練後在邊境上祈禱戰爭不要開始。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204na_platnm_1#7"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，當然，為監正會工作也很有前景的，但那樣的工作內容，我可是一點都不感興趣。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以......"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_223", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  欣特萊雅小姐，請問您有興趣來參加我司的騎士海選嗎？", "name": "騎探"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204na_platnm_1#4"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以當這位玫瑰報業聯合的員工遞上名片時，我帶著略為驚訝的表情，一邊和對方寒暄一邊收下了它。"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "騎士。"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204na_platnm_1#3"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在卡西米爾，誰不想成為騎士呢？"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰不想，在成百上千人的擁簇下，坐享粉絲讚美和大筆收益呢？"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然，一些關於騎士的醜聞時有發生，有些騎士甚至會在一夜間變得默默無聞，但這和我又有什麼關係？"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能使一手好弓，外貌也不算差，最重要的，是我願遵從公司的安排。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204na_platnm_1#8"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要能成為騎士，就算打不過對方，最後像群月騎士團那樣，唱唱歌跳跳舞，趁著年輕多賺一些然後早早退休，或許也是個不錯的選擇。"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G09", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最終，我拿下了玫瑰報業集團當年的騎士海選亞軍，順利獲得了一份夢寐以求的合約。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於冠軍，那個一頭金色碎髮，全身散發著太陽味的男人......"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼說呢，他實在是......太過符合卡西米爾人對於庫蘭塔的想像了，出身也不錯，估計玫瑰早已經內定他作為冠軍了。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使沒有內定，想要在一場大型海選上擊敗他，也還是挺困難的。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少在觀眾投票上就絕對贏不了。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#8"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算啦，也沒什麼好抱怨的。"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今後的路還長著，說不定，我會比他先拿到騎士封號。"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_arena_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_222", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您可以放心，欣特萊雅小姐，這次真的可以獲得騎士封號了。", "name": "經紀人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_222"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我已經向總部確認過，您現在是處理優先順序最高的簽約獨立騎士。", "name": "經紀人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_222"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  近期比賽場數可能會削減，但會大量安排您在媒體上出鏡。", "name": "經紀人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_222"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  只要再等幾個月，獲得了封號，您就是玫瑰新一批次中力推的封號騎士了！", "name": "經紀人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_222"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯，好，謝謝。", "name": "欣特萊雅"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經不是第一次聽到這種許諾了。"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼遠大未來，星光閃耀，玫瑰報業的全力支持。"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他自己似乎都已經沉浸在了這種幻象裡，比他負責的獨立騎士還要相信這些許諾。"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#5"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，這位經紀人性格很好，很刻苦，總是在盡心盡力為我奔波。"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，說實話。"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經對成為騎士這件事有些厭倦了。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#7"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管還沒獲得騎士封號，但一位正式騎士生涯中會遇到的問題，我卻早就碰了個遍。"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "指名要在比賽中放水這種已經是最基礎的了，除了要打得不像假賽這一點比較累人，其他倒還好。"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少還沒被人識破，因此失去騎士資格。"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於應付毫無根據的花邊緋聞，還有被迫接受隨意變動的賽事安排這種事，實在太累人了。"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#5"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只因為我是這一期獨立騎士中的種子選手，所以就得這樣被呼來喊去嗎？"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "騎士到底是什麼？"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "商品嗎？商品至少能買定離手後塵埃落定。"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我呢？"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果說最近還有什麼好消息的話，就是我的騎士封號申請已經被監正院公示了。"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵啊......漫長的獨立騎士生涯，終於要臨近尾聲了。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很快，我就能獲得自己的騎士封號，獲得自己的徽記，然後出現在大街小巷的看板上了吧。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前從來沒有人在這個環節被篩下去的，也就是說......"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打完眼前這場比賽後，我就可以等著獲得封號，成為正式騎士了吧。"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然這一場，“獨立騎士欣特萊雅”的勝負早已被決定了——"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是落敗哦。"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_hotel", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#6", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天那一場的庫蘭塔，怎麼回事？"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我都已經裝作體力不支落敗了，也向裁判示意了，他怎麼還在攻擊我？"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是他作為勝者的權利嗎？在明知自己勝券在握的情況下把我像寵物羽獸一樣攆著全賽場亂跑，肆意羞辱我，讓我出醜？"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是......要不是裝作受傷這件事不能被觀眾發現，我一定——"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#7"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許父親說的對，作為騎士，就是去賽場上受辱的。"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為不甘受辱的人，要嘛用戰錘把這規則下的敵人全部砸碎，要嘛就——"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在一篇新聞報導後消失得無影無蹤。"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_arena_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天是玫瑰報業集團簽約的獨立騎士們上綜藝節目的日子。"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "集團租用了一整座競技場來拍攝節目，甚至還請來了幾位近日熱門的封號騎士。"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是在排練開始前，來了隊不速之客。"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_216", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們把所有騎士帶到角落裡，挨個詢問搜查。"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他們的厲聲喝斥下，騎士們就像枯萎的花草那樣縮在地上，生怕被無胄盟的人盯上。"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使是幾位脾氣不好的騎士，也沒像平時那樣飛揚跋扈，而是低眉順眼，全力配合無胄盟的調查。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是......騎士殺手。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在看著幾位騎士精神崩潰，聽到幾則情急之下脫口而出的驚爆猛料後，無胄盟帶走了一位騎士。"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而今天的活動，則在延遲四小時後重新開始錄製。"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於那位被帶走的騎士？我不知道，我再也沒聽說過和他有關的任何資訊。"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_hotel", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在那場意外發生後沒多久，我接到了一通電話。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘀嘀，嘀嘀"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呼......你好。", "name": "欣特萊雅"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你好，獨立騎士欣特萊雅，恭喜你即將成為封號騎士。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我不知道你是怎麼獲得這個終端號碼的，但如果是商業合作，請找我的經紀人去談，謝謝。", "name": "欣特萊雅"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  看來你並不熱愛現在這份的工作，你的語氣裡充滿了疲憊。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我能提供更適合你的工作。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  只要通過一個簡單的測試，你就能獲得它。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我仍處於困惑和猶豫的時候，終端那頭的男人繼續說到。"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  競技場太過狹窄了，不是嗎？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  箭在你手上只要稍稍一撥，就能從賽場的這頭到那頭。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而我提供的這份工作，不僅薪資能和騎士們媲美，自由度也更高。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  只要你想，欣特萊雅小姐，你的箭能夠洞穿大騎士領的夜幕。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  期待你的回應。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "掛斷之後，他發送了一個地址到我的終端上。"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不知道那裡究竟有什麼，試煉又需要我去做什麼，但......"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“只要你想，欣特萊雅小姐，你的箭能夠洞穿大騎士領的夜幕。”"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#8"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，聽上去可比拍廣告要有意思多了。"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G07", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我到達了他發送的地址，那是一家花店，老闆見到我之後，就從店裡捧出了一束鮮花。"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "花束上的留言寫著一個地址，一些資訊，還有一個名字。"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上一位對手的名字，那個無禮庫蘭塔的名字。"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "花束中藏著一支箭，軍用規格三棱箭，沒有生產廠商，沒有出廠編號。"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能看到這些，說明我已獲得一個組織的初步信任。"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這也意味著，我沒有選擇的餘地了。"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在受到“他們”的邀請後，怎麼可能再回去當騎士？"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要嘛完成測試，要嘛第二天上報紙。"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#6"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我都能預料到報紙標題了——“獨立騎士欣特萊雅因意外在家中逝世”。"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，這根本算不上選項啊......"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G05", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不喜歡殺戮，但現在，我有許多理由讓那個正在落地玻璃窗前享受自助按摩沙發的男人永遠閉上嘴巴。"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "似乎是為了讓我心安，資料上列舉了這位獨立騎士的斑斑劣跡——"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不服從公司安排，私自收取退賽費卻依舊在賽場上打敗了對手，羞辱公司董事。"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一條，都明明可以讓他在公開場合受到法律裁決，但因為他的姓氏，不會有人去這麼做。"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人想得罪一位古老家族的紈絝子弟。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正是因為這個原因，卡西米爾才會需要騎士殺手吧。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#7"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這樣想著，屏息，凝神，拉滿弓弦——"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_arrow_h"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 80.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三棱箭劃出一道弧線，在落地窗上開了個口，穿過他的眉心，他的沙發，最後沒入昂貴的木製地板。"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果還是在競技場上，對付像他這樣的騎士可能要花費很久。"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了要在破甲上花心思外，還得做出許多累贅而多餘的動作去取悅觀眾。"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#8"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在——"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要搭上箭，拉滿弓——"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的工作就完成了。"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沙發還在為他提供按摩，但這位騎士，已經再也無法從沙發上站起身了。"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘀嘀，嘀嘀"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你好。", "name": "欣特萊雅"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  做得很好，欣特萊雅小姐。資訊盤查很到位，任務執行點的選擇也是最優解。至於手法，以你的年齡和天賦來說，也很不錯。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  從今往後，你就是無胄盟的一份子了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我們和玫瑰報業的交涉也剛剛結束，對方同意停止你們間的合約，並支付給你一筆精神損失費。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  明天上午，請來商業聯合會總部大樓，我們會派專人迎接，安排你後續的工作。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好。", "name": "欣特萊雅"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那您，怎麼稱呼？", "name": "欣特萊雅"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你可以叫我——", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  白金。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G03", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是卡西米爾。"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前程似錦的獨立騎士欣特萊雅，在接了個電話，通過一項測試後，就成為了無胄盟白金大位的學徒。"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也正是因為他，我的弓術有了進一步提高。"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起在賽場上短程速射，我更擅長長距離狙擊，白金或許正是看中了這一點，才招攬我成為無胄盟的一員吧。"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而他也教會了我一些未曾設想過的技能。"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "管理、領導、調配、指揮。"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#8"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......難道說，他是在發掘我的領導品質，在培養我成為管理層嗎？"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果能坐在辦公室裡給別人發號施令而不髒了自己的手，也是種不錯的選擇。"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G03", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#2", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三個月之後，民眾們早就忘卻了一位叫做欣特萊雅的獨立騎士。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的職業經紀人轉而為其他通過海選的騎士服務。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的粉絲則被其他騎士的光輝吸引而去。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使是那位最狂熱的粉絲，那個曾經天天守在她住宅門口，只為見她一面的女孩，現在也加入了其他騎士的後援會。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使擦肩而過，她也並沒有認出曾經的偶像。"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好似她從沒存在過一樣。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#7"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在閃耀過後被人遺忘。"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這或許，就是每一位騎士的宿命。"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#5"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但無胄盟不一樣，無胄盟執掌著騎士們的生殺大權，再高傲的騎士見到無胄盟也會立刻變得噤若寒蟬。"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前提是，上頭交代的任務沒有搞砸。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，唉......商業聯合會的董事們可不喜歡在報告裡看到“任務失敗”四個字。"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然，即使是白金大位，也要接受訓斥。"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G03", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_216", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_216"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這就是你們無胄盟的工作態度？", "name": "發言人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_216"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_216"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "無胄盟成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_216"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_216"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我想我肯定和你們強調過，最重要的是訊息，是訊息！", "name": "發言人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_216"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那個騎士是死是活都無所謂，可你們居然讓他把加密訊息發出去了？", "name": "發言人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_216"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "欣特萊雅"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_216"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  “目標佈置了假發報裝置迷惑我方成員，同時用遺體遮掩微型發報器成功傳輸訊息”？", "name": "發言人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_216"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你們就不會多長個心眼？", "name": "發言人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_216"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  人是解決掉了，問題呢？！", "name": "發言人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_216"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我說的問題你們解決了沒有？！", "name": "發言人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_216"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_216"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （抿了抿嘴）", "name": "無胄盟成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_216"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （看向白金大位）", "name": "欣特萊雅"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位發言人罵了有一個多小時了，也不知道這位大人物究竟是時間充足到能夠定下心來慢慢罵人，"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是他就願意花那麼多時間來訓斥無胄盟的雇員們。"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個傢伙想怎麼罵是他的自由，但我更在意的，是另一件事。"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從頭到尾，站在發言人面前的白金沒有一絲辯解和反駁的意願。"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我所認識的他，並不是這樣的人。"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少，他的脾氣絕沒有好到能忍受一個人長時間的辱駡。"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果惹怒一位白金大位，眼前這位柔弱的高級上班族根本沒有活命的機會。"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他還是忍住了。"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不僅咽下了那口氣，還在盡力讓自己的表情看上去顯得順從。"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只因那是一位發言人，只因那個人，是商業聯合會的一員。"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場斥責大會最終持續了整整一小時三十六分鐘二十八秒零三六。"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出席會議的有一位發言人，一位書記員，白金大位，我，還有七名無胄盟成員。"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全程只由他一人發言，至於我們，唉，我們好像連說句話的資格都沒有。"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#5"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從那一天開始，我算是明白了。"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼騎士，什麼無胄盟，說到底，只是商業聯合會的雇員而已，和那些坐在辦公室裡，點頭哈腰寫文書打電話的傢伙們也沒什麼區別。"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是我們手上的活更辛苦，拿的工錢更多。"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅此而已。"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G07", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在某個平常的雨夜，抬手解決掉一位騎士後，青金找上了我。"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_209_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  小天馬，我在找白金，你有看到他嗎？", "name": "“青金”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_209_1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  師父出任務了，青金閣下。", "name": "欣特萊雅"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_209_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是嗎，哈哈。", "name": "“青金”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_209_1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是什麼任務？", "name": "“青金”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_209_1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  他沒有告訴我。", "name": "欣特萊雅"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_209_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那他有告訴過你，他對這次的目標抱有疑問嗎？", "name": "“青金”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_209_1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#7"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒有，閣下，但我能察覺到一點。", "name": "欣特萊雅"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#7"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_209_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "“青金”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_209_1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你很誠實，小天馬。", "name": "“青金”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_209_1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯，既然你願意和我分享白金的秘密，那我也來告訴你一件事吧。", "name": "“青金”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_209_1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  “白金”已經死了，死在他叛逃的路上。", "name": "“青金”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_209_1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#6"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ！", "name": "欣特萊雅"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#6"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "欣特萊雅"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#6"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道他對他的上一個目標有些——動情。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但為了她付出生命，還是出乎了我的意料。"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_209_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  現在這個位置突然空出來，不僅是我，玄鐵們和商業聯合會的董事都會很困擾的。", "name": "“青金”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_209_1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  要不這樣吧，小天馬。", "name": "“青金”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_209_1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你來當白金，怎麼樣？", "name": "“青金”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_209_1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一時間，我都不知道怎樣回答他。"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果回答是，青金會不會抬手殺了我？如果回答不是，我是不是也活不了？"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能呆在那裡，嘴中掉出些遲滯的字句。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#5"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的，我沒有勇氣回答這個問題。"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算我是白金的學徒，有可能接他的班，可他手下的學徒又不只有我一個。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "況且白金剛剛叛變，讓他的學徒成為新白金，於情於理都不合適啊？"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有那幾位老資歷的無胄盟成員，論技術，論指揮能力，哪位不比我強？"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼是我？"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼會是我？"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看著我呆滯的樣子，青金一邊笑，一邊把象徵著“白金”的徽章塞在了我手裡。"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_209_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你不說，我就算你默許了。", "name": "“青金”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_209_1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  新工作要好好幹哦，小白金。", "name": "“青金”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_209_1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#7"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說完，他離開了現場，只留下成為白金的欣特萊雅，和一位倒地的騎士。"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G03", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成為白金後，我才真正理解到他的難處。"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每天，商業聯合會的董事們都在給無胄盟出難題。"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青金會親自負責最優先的任務，而白金，在輔助青金的同時，還要分派人手去解決董事們的其他難題。"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又要管又要帶還得親自上陣，卡西米爾哪有比這更吃力不討好的工作。"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸好，他教的技巧都能用得上。"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在出了幾項小差錯，被幾位發言人罵了兩三次後，我也算是對這份工作有了些瞭解，還能勉強履行作為白金大位的職責。"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#7"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果能辭職，我一定在第一時間給商業聯合會遞上辭呈。"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種煎熬、重負、高風險的工作，誰愛做誰做。"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#5"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜，我沒有選擇權。"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G07", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當一名白金大位有個壞處。"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就是，你永遠不知道屬於商業聯合會的電話會何時響起。"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從大騎士領的中心，商業聯合會總部大樓。"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到移動城市的邊緣，地塊交接處。"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它就像是徘徊在這座城市中的幽靈。"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總能找到一個被稱作白金的可憐人。"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "撥響鈴聲，要求她接通電話，傾聽來自聯合會的聲音。"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#7"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而白金，沒有拒絕的權力。"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是——"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您說。", "name": "白金"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#7"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您好，白金大位，這裡有一項秘密任務要交付給你，請你現在就動身。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#7"}, {"id": 438, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哼......您說吧。", "name": "白金"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我們希望你能讓輝煌盾工業的董事長明天不列席商業聯合會董事會議。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您，您的意思是？！", "name": "白金"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是的，我們希望他從此不再參與任何輝煌盾工業集團相關事務。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  對一位董事下手，我應該沒有這項權力。", "name": "白金"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}, {"id": 448, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這項任務原本是部署給青金的，但他們舉薦你來完成。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  所以，你的電話響了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  任務權限口令為——————", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  請核對。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  核對完畢......無誤。", "name": "白金"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  很好。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}, {"id": 457, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不要讓我們失望。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}, {"id": 458, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#4"}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓一名普通人消失並不難，但讓一名商業聯合會董事不明不白地死去，這可不是一件容易的事。"}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了再次確認，我聯繫上了青金。"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青金告訴我，只要去輝煌盾工業集團總部大樓的董事長休息室完成任務就好。"}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不會是一件艱難的差事，因為上下都打點完畢了，沒有人會阻止我。"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#2"}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "掛斷通訊後，我長長歎了一口氣。"}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟連青金都這麼說了，我又能怎麼辦呢？"}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離天亮只剩下四個小時了。"}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G07", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 475, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 477, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了確保這位董事沒有退路，在前往輝煌盾工業集團總部大樓前我部署了一支無胄盟小隊在他子女的住所周邊。"}}, {"id": 478, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，我從正門進入了這座大樓。"}}, {"id": 479, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正如青金所說，整個輝煌盾工業都為今晚做好了準備。"}}, {"id": 480, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總部大樓敞開，保安被調離，相關探頭全部檢修，一張臨時門禁卡放在前台最顯眼的位置上，而這張卡片——"}}, {"id": 481, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "擁有著直接通往頂層董事長休息室的權限。"}}, {"id": 482, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 483, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 484, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 485, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 486, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 487, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 488, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 489, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當我走進這間，哦不，應該說是這層專屬休息室時，輝煌盾的董事長還在他的大型終端前辛勤工作。"}}, {"id": 490, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他回過神來之前，我扭斷了他的脖頸。"}}, {"id": 491, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確認完目標生命體徵消失後，我向青金彙報了任務情況。"}}, {"id": 492, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照常規流程，聯合會的電話馬上會響起，所以我並沒有著急離開。"}}, {"id": 493, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}}, {"id": 494, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接電話嘛，在哪接不是接呢？"}}, {"id": 495, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我拉開窗簾，透過巨大的落地窗，望向大騎士領燈火不熄的夜晚。"}}, {"id": 496, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 497, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 498, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 499, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G07", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 500, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 501, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我仍是一位學生時，我憧憬著騎士的身份。"}}, {"id": 502, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成為騎士後，我知曉了騎士殺手們的秘密。"}}, {"id": 503, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可成為了無胄盟的幹部，也還是要對商業聯合會的董事言聽計從。"}}, {"id": 504, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而今天，機緣巧合間，一位董事在我手中倒下。"}}, {"id": 505, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父母曾說過，我敏銳的雙眼一定能為家族帶來榮耀。"}}, {"id": 506, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而現在，我看到了什麼？"}}, {"id": 507, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到大騎士領外一片漆黑的荒野。"}}, {"id": 508, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到漫布整個大騎士領的霓虹燈光。"}}, {"id": 509, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到，矗立在城市正中的商業聯合會大樓。"}}, {"id": 510, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有在那之上的璀璨夜空。"}}, {"id": 511, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要能看見，我就能理解。"}}, {"id": 512, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......"}}, {"id": 513, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這商業的高塔之上，城市碾過的土地之下，有一雙看不見的手，操縱著這些董事們。"}}, {"id": 514, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "驅使他們在建築所能到達的頂端，添磚加瓦，繼續建造名為卡西米爾的高塔。"}}, {"id": 515, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像他們只是傀儡，只是僕從，如果有人不稱其心意，就把他換掉。"}}, {"id": 516, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不是第一個，也絕不會是最後一個。"}}, {"id": 517, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這雙手經由商業聯合會，延伸到整個卡西米爾。"}}, {"id": 518, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你還在這片大地上，就逃不過它。"}}, {"id": 519, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 520, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 521, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 522, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 523, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#3"}}, {"id": 524, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 525, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 526, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 527, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 528, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 529, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 530, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哼......", "name": "白金"}}, {"id": 531, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#8"}}, {"id": 532, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 533, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 534, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉......就不能給我點時間發呆嗎......", "name": "白金"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#8"}, {"id": 535, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_204_platnm_1#5"}}, {"id": 536, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 537, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 538, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好累......", "name": "白金"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#5"}, {"id": 539, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好想，放假啊......", "name": "白金"}, "figure_art": "char_204_platnm_1#5"}, {"id": 540, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 541, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 542, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 543, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 544, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 545, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 546, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 547, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 548, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}